    <description>
perl-lsp is a high-performance Language Server Protocol implementation for Perl,
providing advanced IDE features including real-time syntax checking, code completion,
go-to-definition, find references, symbol search, and refactoring support.

## Features

- ~100% Perl syntax coverage
- Real-time syntax checking and diagnostics
- Code completion with type inference
- Go-to-definition and find references
- Symbol search across workspace
- Advanced refactoring operations
- Incremental parsing with <1ms updates
- Cross-file navigation with dual indexing
- Import optimization

## Installation

After installation, configure your editor to use `perl-lsp --stdio`.

## Documentation

See https://github.com/EffortlessMetrics/perl-lsp for full documentation.
